OL,3,CBristol to start charging people
OL,4,Cliving in vans council tax amid rising
OL,5,Ctensions
OL,7,FThe housing crisis is creating a new
OL,8,Fcrisis on the streets as hundreds of
OL,9,Fvan-dwellers crowd out beauty spots
OL,10,Fand frustrate locals, but those who
OL,11,Flive in their vehicles say they have
OL,12,Ffew other options, ITV News
OL,13,FCorrespondent Sangita Lal reports
OL,15,FClifton Downs is a beauty spot that's
OL,16,Fbeen protected for public use since
OL,17,Fthe 1860's.
OL,19,FA 21st-century housing crisis, though,
OL,20,Fhas created a new need.
