OL,4,Cliving in vans council tax amid rising
OL,5,Ctensions
OL,7,FThere are more than 600 van dwellers
OL,8,Facross Bristol, with more than a
OL,9,Fhundred along the Downs.
OL,11,FIt has created tension between those
OL,12,Fliving curbside and residents in the
OL,13,Fsurrounding area.
OL,15,FRecently, Bristol City Council
OL,16,Fallocated derelict land that people
OL,17,Fcould pay to use.
OL,19,FPitches are available on the so-called
OL,20,F"Meanwhile Sites" for van dwellers for
OL,21,Faround #140 a month.
