OL,7,FThis pays for waste removal services,
OL,8,Fa gated entrance and a communal tap.
OL,10,FFrom April 1 though, they'll have to
OL,11,Fpay Band A council tax on top of this
OL,12,Fcharge.
OL,14,FDan Clarke has lived on the Meanwhile
OL,15,FSite for two months. For him, the
OL,16,Fscheme is a really positive step to
OL,17,Fhelp get people away from curb-side
OL,18,Fliving, but the council tax will
OL,19,Fdiscourage people from wanting to move
OL,20,Fthere.
