OL,7,FHe told ITV News: "It does seem
OL,8,Fconfusing, is the priority get the
OL,9,Fvehicle-dwellers paying council tax or
OL,10,Fis the priority to get them off the
OL,11,Froadside.
OL,13,F"If it's going to discourage people
OL,14,Ffrom using the system, it kind of
OL,15,Fseems like they're shooting themselves
OL,16,Fin the foot."
OL,18,FAcross Bristol, tensions have been
OL,19,Frising over the number of van dwellers
OL,20,Fin the city.
