OL,7,FLast year, hundreds protested against
OL,8,Fone of the UK's largest van
OL,9,Fcommunities, with campaigners claiming
OL,10,Fthey were damaging the environment.
OL,12,FZeng has lived in Clifton for two
OL,13,Fdecades. He says it's not the people,
OL,14,Fbut the circumstances they live in
OL,15,Fthat are concerning locals.
OL,17,FHe told ITV News the situation was
OL,18,F"quite depressing and unsafe".
