OL,7,FHe said often the vehicles were dirty
OL,8,Fwith broken windows, and he also said
OL,9,Fmany van-dwellers stored gas for
OL,10,Fcooking outside their vehicles.
OL,12,FZeng said he believed the new council
OL,13,Ftax would "discourage people from
OL,14,Fcoming here because they will have to
OL,15,Fpay money".
