OL,7,FAccording to the charity Crisis, over
OL,8,Fthe last five years, there's been a
OL,9,F30% increase in the number of people
OL,10,Fliving in vehicles as rental prices
OL,11,Fhave continued to rise across the
OL,12,Fcountry.
OL,14,FCrisis CEO Matt Downe told ITV News:
OL,15,F"If you're homeless, then council tax
OL,16,Fdoesn't make much sense."
