OL,3,CBristol to start charging people
OL,4,Cliving in vans council tax amid rising
OL,5,Ctensions
OL,7,FBristol City Council says: "Under UK
OL,8,Flaw, people who live in a caravan or a
OL,9,Fvehicle, on a pitch, as their sole or
OL,10,Fmain residence are liable for council
OL,11,Ftax. This applies to meanwhile sites
OL,12,Fas well as other caravan sites in the
OL,13,Fcity. We have written to people living
OL,14,Fon our sites to let them know that
OL,15,Fthey will be charged from April 1 2026.
