OL,7,F"We are working closely with people
OL,8,Fliving on our meanwhile sites to
OL,9,Fexplore any support available to them,
OL,10,Fincluding the Council Tax Reduction
OL,11,FScheme, and offering help to apply for
OL,12,Fany discounts and exemptions they are
OL,13,Fentitled to.
OL,15,F"At a time when we are trying to move
OL,16,Fpeople away from kerbside living, we
OL,17,Fwant to make living on meanwhile sites
OL,18,Fan affordable and viable option for
OL,19,Fvehicle dwellers."
